creator: Vestpark
descriptionHtml:
VestPark UNUM is a comprehensive parking management system. As a user you will automatically be read in and out of the parking area and will be able to seamlessly pay for your parking by registrering a payment card.
If you have special agreements, you will also be able to manage your agreements in the UNUM app as well as register guests
descriptionShort: Pay for your parking, manage your agreements and register guest parking

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Improved instructions
- Small bug fixes and text changes
- Made menu be open by default on login
